{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":12,"day":18}],"page_start":6,"page_end":6,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"毛主席看了俺的枪山东柳琴书","authors":["宁春廷〖HH/换行〗DW：济南部队业余演出队"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"（幕启，锣鼓喧天）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众：（在幕后唱）哎嗨！哎"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嗨！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（小战士兴高采烈地跑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小战士：（白）好消息！好消"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"息！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众：（跑上）什么好消息？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小战士：你们看，班长回来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（班长带枪欢快地上）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众：班长回来啦！班长！你看"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到毛主席了吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小战士：不但看到了毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席还看了俺班长的枪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哩！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众：真的吗？班长你快说说"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"班长：好！我说说！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（唱）咳嗨！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众：咳嗨！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俺班长进京比武得胜利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带来了惊人的好消息！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"班长：毛主席看了这支枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夸奖俺练出的好武艺。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小战士：（白）毛主席他老人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家怎么说的？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众：是呀！毛主席他……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小战士：别吵吵，别着急。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（唱）听班长一点一滴——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众：一点一滴说详细呀，那个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说详细呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小战士：（白）班长，你快说"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众：班长，你快说说呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"班长：（唱）那天是六月十五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好天气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有两个太阳照大地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一轮红日刚出山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在面前出现了毛主席。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众：毛主席呀，毛主席呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"班长：毛主席走上了检阅台，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全场都欢呼万岁万岁万岁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众：毛主席！毛主席！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"班长：（白）我心里不知怎么"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好啦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（唱）恐怕打不出好成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小战士：（白）班长，你心里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"慌吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士甲：班长，你千万可别慌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（小战士正想说，被大家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拦住）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"班长：（唱）轮到了我来射"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"击，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看准目标把枪举。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众：把枪举，把枪举！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"班长：我心儿跳，心儿急，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我把那靶子当美帝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心怀仇恨稳住打。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众：稳住打，稳住打！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（数板）别心跳，别心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"急。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"班长：我看准目标扣扳机。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（枪响）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（唱）报靶的红旗高高"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪枪打在靶心里！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众：枪枪打在靶心里呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪枪打在靶心里！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小战士：（白）班长，你打得"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真棒啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众：班长打得真好！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士甲：班长，毛主席一定很"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高兴吧？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"班长：（唱）我射击完毕刚站"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就只见罗总长把靶子递给"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"了毛主席。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（数板）毛主席看看靶子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对俺微微笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弄得俺不知怎么好哩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我张着嘴儿说不出话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（唱）千言万语从哪说"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众：毛主席的身体可健康？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"班长：红光满面好身体。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众：毛主席的话儿你听的懂？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"班长：句句都印在俺心里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小战士：（白）班长，毛主席"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎么看你的枪？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众：是啊，怎么看你的枪啊？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"班长：（唱）我刚刚走到队列"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"罗总长来到俺这里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把俺的枪拿过去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双手递给了毛主席！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席接过俺的枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看枪管来看枪机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞄一瞄来扳扳机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望着枪点头很欢喜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（数板）毛主席夸俺枪法"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把枪放在俺手里；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓励俺好好练本领，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俺心里不知说啥好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热泪涌到了眼眶里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小战士：（白）班长，把枪给"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看看。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众：（传看）看到了枪，就想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到了毛主席。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"班长：（唱）回来后夜里睡觉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合不上眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日夜想念毛主席。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自从您领导闹革命那天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您教导俺把枪杆子握在咱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿起枪秋收起义分田地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿起枪井冈山上插红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿起枪打败了日本鬼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿起枪打败了蒋匪得胜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"利。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任凭敌人多狡猾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪杆子握得紧紧的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管革命多困难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您领导从胜利走向胜利！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众：（争着看枪，唱）毛主席"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呀，毛主席！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看到了枪想起了您。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想起了您，浑身上下增力"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"气。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您的话句句记在俺心里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人的手里拿着刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们把本领练得棒棒的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人一天不消灭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这支枪永远握在俺手里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远握紧这支枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚决把革命干到底！"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}